definition: to get rid of/to exclude/to eliminate/to remove/to delete/to strip out/to extract

to go/to go to (a place)/(of a time etc) last/just passed/to send/to remove/to get rid of/to reduce/to be apart from in space or time/to die (euphemism)/to play (a part)/(when used either before or after a verb) to go in order to do sth/(after a verb of motion indicates movement away from the speaker)/(used after certain verbs to indicate detachment or separation)

to fall/to drop/to lag behind/to lose/to go missing/to reduce/fall (in prices)/to lose (value, weight etc)/to wag/to swing/to turn/to change/to exchange/to swap/to show off/to shed (hair)/(used after certain verbs to express completion, fulfillment, removal etc)

sentences.english: Let me actually get rid of that for just a moment.
sentences.chinese: 我們先去掉那個一會兒。

sentences.english: Now you can drop the subscripts if you prefer.
sentences.chinese: 現在如果你樂意，可以去掉下標。

sentences.english: A woman, after marriage, usually drops her surname and takes that of her husband.
sentences.chinese: 女人在婚後往往去掉自己的姓氏而冠以夫姓。

sentences.english: Second, it requires us to remove older data and store it elsewhere.
sentences.chinese: 其次，它要求我們去掉比較舊的數據並在別處存儲。

sentences.english: Clean well the scratch with alcohol.
sentences.chinese: 可以用酒精把那個擦痕去掉。

sentences.english: This should get rid of your compilation errors.
sentences.chinese: 這樣應該可以去掉編輯錯誤。

sentences.english: An immediate cold water souse may remove the black spot from your shirt.
sentences.chinese: 立即放在涼水裏浸泡可能會去掉襯衫上的黑點。

sentences.english: You may wonder why having a horn cut off requires anaesthetics.
sentences.chinese: 你可能會覺得奇怪，爲什麼去掉牛角需要麻醉？

sentences.english: Rerank the viable functions excluding the function template instantiations .
sentences.chinese: 重新排列去掉函數模板實例的可行函數。

sentences.english: Last year, the company said it was removing dibutyl phthalate .
sentences.chinese: 去年，該公司稱要從指甲油中去掉鄰苯二甲酸二丁酯。

sentences.english: Discard the cinnamon, thyme and bay leaves.
sentences.chinese: 去掉肉桂，百里香和月桂樹葉。

sentences.english: Make stalks into match sticks about 3 inches in length.
sentences.chinese: 根莖去掉粗皮後切成3寸左右長段。

sentences.english: Well, aren't you glad now that you get rid of that old tree?
sentences.chinese: 好啦，難道你現在不因爲去掉了那棵古樹而欣喜嗎？

sentences.english: Come back to it and make it more beautiful by whittling away the unnecessary.
sentences.chinese: 重新開始，將繁縟的細節去掉，使作品更加完美。
怎樣才能把血管瘤去掉？
